asset.hookText:
Tesla Roadster crossing China during his around the world trip in 80 days. 80edays video donde el Tesla Roadster cruza China. Rafael de Mestre durchfährt mit seinem 100% elektrischen Roadster China inklusive der Wüste Gobi.
On this segment he overtakes Antonin and Xavier driving with an 100% electric Citroen C-Zero.
